By: Bâyazîd al-Bistâmî
---
’I thought that I had arrived at the very Throne of God and I said to it：
‘O Throne, they tell us that God rests upon thee.’ ‘O Bâyazîd,’
replied the Throne, ‘we are told here that He dwells in a humble heart.’
